summary: Highly motivated and adaptable professional with a strong background in retail management and a burning passion for a career pivot into the dynamic world of Information Technology. Eager to leverage my transferable skills in customer service, problem-solving, and teamwork skills acquired in the retail industry, I am committed to embracing new challenges and becoming a valuable asset in the IT field. Equipped with a solid foundation in technology through self-directed learning and completion of relevant online courses and certifications, I am determined to contribute my enthusiasm for IT and dedication to continuous learning to drive innovation and efficiency in this fast-paced industry.
